public interface TestBaseInterface<RE extends IRingElement<RE>>

This is used to enforce that tests use a generic method to obtain a factory for the base type to be tested.

getFactory

IRingElementFactory<RE> getFactory()
This method provides access to the factory of the base type. This is used to make tests generic for all types.
